import sys

def main():
    s = sys.stdin.readline().rstrip()
    t = sys.stdin.readline().rstrip()

    if can_eq(s, t):
        print('Yes')
    else:
        print('No')

def can_eq(s, t):
    if len(s) != len(t): return False
    s_list = list(s)
    t_list = list(t)
    s_list.sort()
    t_list.sort()
    return s_list == t_list

if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
